        "subject": "LU-1323 llite: find_vma() should be protected by mmap_sem",
        "message": "LU-1323 llite: find_vma() should be protected by mmap_sem\n\nIt had been wrongly protected by page_table_lock since 2004.\n\nLustre-commit: 5eb306e7634ab825306b850226ef9b199a888759\nLustre-change:  http://review.whamcloud.com/2543\n\nLU-5221 vvp: release mmap_sem in error case\n\nThe mmap_sem is downed in vvp_mmap_locks, but in case of\nerror from cl_io_lock_alloc_add, it is not upped.\n\nCredit to Paul Casella at Cray for finding this.\n\nLustre-commit: dece70280b7075c4ca39472ad48e72d696b6fcf8\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/10741\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@whamcloud.com>\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <paf@cray.com>\nSigned-off-by: Niu Yawei <yawei.niu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I188bb5c4008065fe8dc3bf6d108fb20e8a3016a4\n"
      },
